<F P=100> INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Arab-Israeli Talks </F>
<H3> <TI>   Israeli-Palestinian Self-Rule Agreement Signed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Israeli-Palestinian Self-Rule Agreement Signed </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    MENA: 'Arafat, Rabin Refuse To Sign Map </H4>

<F P=102> NC0405093794 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0926 GMT 4 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0405093794 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 4 May (MENA)--Palestinian President Yasir 
'Arafat refused to sign the map attached to the self-rule 
agreement delineating the area of Jericho. 
  When Israeli Prime Minister Rabin noticed that President 
'Arafat did not sign, he consulted with Foreign Minister Peres, 
who in turn consulted with President 'Arafat. Rabin then 
refused to sign the map. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

