  [Text] The German charge d'affaires in Tehran met the 
deputy foreign minister for Europe and America affairs this 
afternoon and handed over a message from German Chancellor 
Helmut Kohl to Mr. Hashemi-Rafsanjani. 
  In his message the German chancellor welcomes the deepening 
