  Al-Hudaybi spoke to IRNA from his hospital bed where he is 
recovering from an illness. The Muslim Brotherhood, the most 
powerful Islamic movement in the arab world, is strongly opposed 
to the so-called Middle East peace process. [passage omitted] 

