<F P=103> NC0405114494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The 10 Palestinian opposition groups, the Hamas 
movement, and the Palestinian Islamic Jihad have declared a 
strike in the Palestinian camps in the Sidon area, the 'Ayn 
al-Hulwah camp, and the al-Miyah wa Miyah camp. Shops inside 
the camps closed and classes in United Nations Relief and Works 
Agency schools were suspended to protest the signing of the 
agreement between Israel and the PLO in Cairo today. Car tires 
were set on fire at the entrances to the camps this morning. 

