<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The government is taking appropriate steps to 
counter the situation arising out of threat of the supply of 
F-16 aircrafts to Pakistan by the United States. In a written 
reply in the Rajya Sabha today, the minister of state for 
defense, Mr. Mallikarjun, assured the house that the government 
is closely monitoring the matter concerning the supply of these 
aircrafts and steps are being taken to counter it. 

</TEXT>

